{"kind":"FETCH","data":{"headers":{},"body":"{\"_id\":\"69e1f47dafffda63ef451aee\",\"heading\":\"Purpose-Driven Advisory.\",\"subheading\":\"Outcome-focused delivery for individuals, corporates, and government entities.\",\"description\":\"VidhiSatya.com is established to offer a helping hand to clients facing targets and challenges in their working. Consultation is provided on solicitation basis with fee and expenses borne by the individual, corporate, or government entity seeking advice. Our founder's 35+ years of experience is offered as a valuable asset at fair pricing so clients can make the best use of limited time.\",\"vision\":\"To help clients execute work in a duly compliant manner while remaining truthful in every aspect.\",\"mission\":\"To deliver practical consultation and advisory support for individuals, corporates, and governments with clear action pathways.\",\"philosophy\":\"Vidhi Satya combines two Hindi words: 'Vidhi' (Vidhivat, complied in all aspects) and 'Satya' (truthful).\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://placehold.co/1000x800/0F172A/F8FAFC?text=About+Vidhi+Satya\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-17T08:51:09.507Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-17T08:51:09.507Z\",\"__v\":0}","status":200,"url":""},"revalidate":30,"tags":["public-about"]}